title: Treacherous (Taylor's Version)
description:
Ignore the red flags and run straight into the arms of danger! That is what Taylor is singing about in this song, but others have a more sexier interpretation of it. We break down all of the theories, speculations and the different meanings behind this song!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There's lots of ways to reach us!
